      "Text": "Security update for xen",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for xen fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2024-2201: Mitigation for Native Branch History Injection (XSA-456, bsc#1222453)\n- CVE-2023-46842: HVM hypercalls may trigger Xen bug check (XSA-454, bsc#1221984)\n- CVE-2024-31142: Fixed incorrect logic for BTC/SRSO mitigations (XSA-455, bsc#1222302)\n- Upstream bug fixes (bsc#1027519)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
